OL,5, The billionaire founder of the outdoor 
OL,6, fashion brand Patagonia has given away 
OL,7, his company to a charitable trust.     
OL,9,FYvon Chouinard said any profit not     
OL,10,Freinvested in running the business     
OL,11,Fwould go to fighting climate change.   
OL,13,FThe label has amassed a cult following 
OL,14,Fdue to sustainability moves like       
OL,15,Fguaranteeing its clothes for life and  
OL,16,Foffering reasonably priced repairs.    
OL,18,FIt is famous for an advert titled      
OL,19,F"Don't buy this jacket" asking shoppers
OL,20,Fto consider costs to the environment.  
